Placeholder for Jupyter notebooks used during exploratory data analysis.

Expected notebooks (create as needed during development):

  eda_mimiciv.ipynb
    Exploratory analysis of MIMIC-IV triage data: distributions of vital
    signs, ED dispositions, age demographics, missing value patterns.
    Used to inform feature engineering decisions.

  eda_nfhs5.ipynb
    Exploratory analysis of NFHS-5 Indian household health data:
    child anthropometry distributions, anemia prevalence by state,
    regional health patterns. Used for Indian data augmentation strategy.

  fl_convergence_plots.ipynb
    Visualization of FL simulation results: convergence curves for
    FedAvg vs FedProx vs SCAFFOLD, Byzantine robustness heatmaps,
    gossip protocol effectiveness. Generates figures for the research paper.

  rag_eval.ipynb
    Manual evaluation of RAG retrieval quality: sample queries,
    retrieved chunks, reranker scores, LLM synthesis quality.
    Used for iterative RAG pipeline tuning.
